ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
Immigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectManitoba Contribution Agreement on Resettlement service provisions to high needs refugees
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the Government of MANITOBA, in order to provide resettlement service provisions to high needs refugees, for a period of two years beginning on the date of signing by the last of the parties to do so.
